and how much variation there is around the mean on this test.

15
00:01:04,980 --> 00:01:09,329
Clearly, this would not give me useful information about what the average performance on the

16
00:01:09,329 --> 00:01:13,950
test would likely be for when I use it with university students.

17
00:01:13,950 --> 00:01:18,990
The population that you standardise the test on has to be relevant for the people who you’ll

18
00:01:18,990 --> 00:01:20,340
