19
00:01:20,340 --> 00:01:23,040
This was a problem early on for a lot of tests.

20
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:27,690
It&#39;s certainly the case now that many tests are still standardised on limited sets of

21
00:01:27,690 --> 00:01:28,690
